  "message": "fix: add npm ci to leaderboard workflow + git hash + fresh data (#1372)\n\n- Add 'npm ci' step \u2014 profiles script needs wink-nlp which was never\n  installed, causing all runs since Apr 9 to fail (leaderboard stale)\n- Add continue-on-error to profiles step so leaderboard still commits\n  if profiles fail\n- Add git_hash to leaderboard.json and display subtly in bottom right\n- Include fresh leaderboard data (fixes stale scores)\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
